sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant W as Photon-Web Wallet (Chrome)
    participant API as Node.js Gateway (Nginx)
    participant UN as User RLN Node (Port 3002)
    participant MN as Master RLN Node (Port 3001)
    participant PX as RGB Proxy (Consignments)
    participant BC as Bitcoin Core (Regtest)

    Note over W, MN: Step 1: Initiating the Transfer
    W->>API: POST /pay-lightning (invoice + x-photon-key)
    API->>UN: Command: send_asset_payment(invoice)

    rect rgb(255, 243, 205)
    Note over UN, MN: Step 2: The Lightning Handshake (Instant)
    UN->>MN: Peer-to-Peer Payment (HTLC)
    MN-->>UN: Pre-image (Settlement Proof)
    end

    rect rgb(209, 236, 241)
    Note over UN, PX: Step 3: RGB Asset Proof (Privacy Layer)
    UN->>PX: Upload PHO Consignment
    MN->>PX: Fetch & Validate Consignment
    end

    Note over UN, BC: Step 4: Verification
    UN->>BC: Verify Taproot Anchor (Is the coin still there?)
    BC-->>UN: Verified (Confirmed at Height 578)

    Note over W: Step 5: Success State
    UN-->>API: Status: SUCCESS (Hash: 69018fc3...)
    API-->>W: Update UI: 9.00 PHO Outbound / 1.00 PHO Inbound
